    All Classes and Interfaces

    Class
    Description
    AlertBox
    AlertBox class for displaying alert and confirmation dialogs in the Battleship game.
    AlertBox.AlertType
    Enum representing the types of alerts that can be shown.
    Board
    Board class representing the game board and managing the state of the Battleship game.
    Board.State
    Enum representing the state of a cell on the game board.
    FileCRUD
    FileCRUD class for performing Create, Read, Update, and Delete operations on a text file.
    Game
    Game class representing the logic and state of a Battleship game.
    GameController
    GameController class for managing the main game logic and user interactions in the Battleship game.
    GameView
    GameView class for displaying the main game window in the Battleship game.
    IAlert
    IAlert interface for displaying alert dialogs in the Battleship game.
    MachineViewController
    MachineViewController class for managing the machine's and player's boards in the Battleship game.
    MachineViewView
    MachineViewView class for displaying the machine and player boards in the Battleship game.
    Main
    Main class for launching the Battleship game application using JavaFX.
    Path
    Path class containing constants for FXML resource paths used in the Battleship game.
    PlacementController
    PlacementController class for managing the placement of ships on the player's board in the Battleship game.
    PlacementView
    PlacementView class for displaying the ship placement window in the Battleship game.
    Serialization
    Serialization utility class for serializing and deserializing objects to and from a file in the Battleship game.
    Ship
    Ship class representing a ship in the Battleship game.
    Ship.Direction
    Enum representing the direction of the ship.
    Ship.Type
    Enum representing the type of the ship.
    StartController
    StartController class for managing the start view and initial user interactions in the Battleship game.
    StartView
    StartView class for displaying the start window in the Battleship game.
